=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對象對我有無feel<br />\n同曖昧對象有無機會<br />\n有無機會複合<br />\n同男女朋友會唔會長久<br />\n通常我準備占你果陣會hi 你，你見到覆下我，當雙方ONLINE我先會占<br />\n無格式需要，你覺得重要就同我講，通常留性別同問題就得"},{"pid":"307b0c269151ab3ac8e25ba64c2083b3bb1c447b","tid":1182142,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab520ab095178ebf2856b41347ebc41bcef57031","tid":1182142,"uid":155283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f3c498323d6a601ba2e3d24a85c608032f2bc4","tid":1182142,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec046507d1afac94f7962f3c5bb3d82b1fdbb8e","tid":1182142,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d351a039495a62acd7a7c90d0d9930eb91a3c8f","tid":1182142,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8f3da8ee0937081a35e7a3a3e57cafbb70906f","tid":1182142,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55dcb982032e323c1fe89fcb5d80deaef2841f5","tid":1182142,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d898d63468b21c8efb9e74140c95c58b7845ba4","tid":1182142,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi